Package civitas.celestis.object

Class ImmovableObject

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.object.BaseObject
civitas.celestis.object.ImmovableObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable, Physical, Renderable, Tickable, Unique
public class ImmovableObject extends BaseObject
An immovable object's location and rotation cannot be changed after instantiation. While immovable objects still have acceleration and rate of rotation, they will only affect the counterparty object of a collision.
